d on the novel hawaii  centennial  tv miniseries based on the novel centennial  caravans  film starring anthony quinn based on the novel caravans  space  tv miniseries based on the novel space  james a micheners texas  tv miniseries based on the novel texas  south pacific  television movie based on the rodgers and hammerstein musical in turn based on the novel tales of the south pacific  see alsoedit list of bestselling novels in the united states edward rutherfurd referencesedit  michener the american heritage dictionary of the english language fourth ed houghton mifflin    a b c d e f g h i albin krebs october   james michener author of novels that sweep through the history of places is dead the new york times retrieved november     michener james  presidential lottery penguin random house retrieved march     a b c d e f g james michener biography pennsylvania center for the book penn state university libraries   biographical sketch james a michener papers university of miami library   may kalen october   unc celebrating michener library’s first  years university of colorado     michener michener library   michener james a  return to paradise random house   beers paul b march   pennsylvania politics today and yesterday the tolerable accommodation penn state university press p  isbn    a b c get me michener at raffles the new paper singapore september     hayes john michael  james a michener a biography bobbsmerrill p    hayes p   james michener biography bookragscom retrieved may     centennial the complete miniseries dvdtalkcom retrieved march     james a michener a bibliography charles parkhurst rare books inc retrieved march     the th academy awards  nominees and winners academy of motion picture arts and sciences ampas retrieved august     james a michener art museum michenerartmuseumorg   journey prize mcclellandcom   the michener center for writers and its master of fine arts program at the university of texas at austin utexasedu retrieved may     the miche